(k+1)^2
2(n  +1)
 \begin{align} \sum_{k=1}^n\log\left(\frac{k(k+2)}{(k+1)^2}\right) &=\sum_{k=1}^n\log\left(\frac{k}{k+1}\right)-\sum_{k=1}^n\log\left(\frac{k+1}{k+2}\right)\\ &=\sum_{k=1}^n\log\left(\frac{k}{k+1}\right)-\sum_{k=2}^{n+1}\log\left(\frac{k}{k+1}\right)\\ &=\log\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)-\log\left(\frac{n+1}{n+2}\right)\\ &=\log\left(\frac{n+2}{2n+2}\right) \end{align} 
